  "title": "NextJS app router SSR - filters are empty on server",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\nWhen using useRange/useCurrentRefinements/useRefinementLists, etc. They all return empty items on the server and on the initial rendering, only after a couple re-renders in the client it populates the values with the correct values.\n\nuseHits is the only one that seems to be actually returning the correct values both on client and on server side\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\nNextjs app router example is not working on code sandox, both local and in codesandox its getting stucked loading.\n\nHappy to give a reproduction example if we manage to get that working\n\n### Live reproduction\n\n-\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\n-\n\n### Package version\n\n-\n\n### Operating system\n\n_No response_\n\n### Browser\n\n_No response_\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [x] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
